  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe Reactive REST Client is what we promote to users for making downstream HTTP calls.\r\nCurrently there is no micrometer metrics integration for this, but it would be awesome to have metrics for each named client so users can easily identify issues with each service separately.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\nAt a very high level, we'll need to plug in a proper implementation of `HttpClientMetrics` that will be able to disambiguate between calls originating from the REST client and delegate to micrometer.",
